<br />In <em>Super Street Fighter II</em>, Dee Jay's pant leg was originally going to say MANTIS until Capcom's artists realized that this would make Dee Jay's CHR data 50% bigger (need separate data for left and right views of bottom half). So they changed it to MAXIMUM for great symmetry.

		

